Package: com.zeshan.phoneaura
Name: PhoneAura
Version: 0.4.4
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64e
Description: RootHide iOS 16 full-stage overlap repair. Covers Apple’s entire root Phone screen with one opaque Concept D stage, separates the header from tab content inside that stage, prevents stock titles and first rows from appearing behind Favorites or Recents, limits runtime hooks to tab and navigation controllers, preserves Settings controls, and restores Apple contact-detail and active-call screens.
Maintainer: Next Solution
Author: Next Solution
Section: Tweaks
Depends: firmware (>= 16.0), mobilesubstrate, preferenceloader
